{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286889, "create_time": 1657462469, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "能不能先说清楚钱去哪了？到底是不是地方政府拿走了？", "timestamp": 1657462469}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286890, "create_time": 1657462496, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "如果是财政拿走了，用财政的钱去赔岂不是天经地义？当然地方财政也没钱就是了", "timestamp": 1657462496}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286892, "create_time": 1657462556, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "说清楚发生了什么事情，让违法的人承担应有的责任", "timestamp": 1657462556}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286897, "create_time": 1657462610, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 如果不是财政拿走了，而是被某些个人拿走了的话呢", "timestamp": 1657462610}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286902, "create_time": 1657462674, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "政府现在不赔，之后中小银行大规模挤兑，那就不是赔能解决问题了", "timestamp": 1657462674}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286904, "create_time": 1657462696, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: 恐怕是大环境造成的。放到经济好的时候，钱怎么也能还上，现在就...", "timestamp": 1657462696}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286906, "create_time": 1657462809, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re 洞主: 现在遮遮掩掩的，就不像是某个人拿走的", "timestamp": 1657462809}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286918, "create_time": 1657463071, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 我觉得不可能，我不信最后调查结论会是如此。个人得胆子多大才能做出这个事出来，而且图什么，个人要这么多钱有什么用，我无法理解", "timestamp": 1657463071}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286919, "create_time": 1657463076, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 不过确实很难想象钱是被财政拿走的，政府把一个银行的钱，偷偷转到财政的账户上？这感觉都不太好操作呀", "timestamp": 1657463076}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286928, "create_time": 1657463233, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re 洞主: 也可能是默许的吧，地方政府的欠债问题，还有核酸检测花费，挪用点钱都不算啥", "timestamp": 1657463233}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286929, "create_time": 1657463234, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 很好操作，随便举个例子，地方政府把土地使用权高价卖给房地产商，收一笔土地出让金，同时让银行发贷款给房地产商。储户的钱就通过银行、房地产商到了地方财政的手里", "timestamp": 1657463234}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286937, "create_time": 1657463425, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re 洞主: 政府成立城投公司（地方投融资平台）搞建设，然后城投公司从银行贷款或者发行城投债融资。城投公司入不敷出，还不上贷款，不能兑付城投债。然后银行贷出去的钱收不回来", "timestamp": 1657463425}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286942, "create_time": 1657463539, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 在这个过程中，银行图什么呢？", "timestamp": 1657463539}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286944, "create_time": 1657463587, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 银行为什么要贷款给城投公司呢？", "timestamp": 1657463587}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286949, "create_time": 1657463675, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re 洞主: 城投公司路子这么野，如果从四大行之类的大银行贷款，想通过审核是很难的。所以一般都是从地方银行（比如城商行、村镇银行）贷款，这些银行只需要地方政府打声招呼就能发贷了", "timestamp": 1657463675}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286955, "create_time": 1657463863, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 打声招呼就能发贷？！", "timestamp": 1657463863}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286956, "create_time": 1657463889, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re 洞主: 银行放贷当然是图利息，当然城投公司可能还不上，但小银行一般也只能贷款给比较劣质的客户。因为风险较高，这些客户也必须支付比较高的利息", "timestamp": 1657463889}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286958, "create_time": 1657463951, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re 洞主: 如果是地方银行（特别是村镇银行），难道能拒绝地方政府的要求？", "timestamp": 1657463951}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286960, "create_time": 1657463974, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re 洞主: 如果真是这样的话，那我觉得“政府打声招呼就发贷”确实是个严重的问题", "timestamp": 1657463974}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286973, "create_time": 1657464338, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 假如我是银行管理层的话，感觉这个风险有点大呀。假如不出事，银行收到的利息收入确实更多了，可万一真出了事，不仅整个银行要蒙受损失，自己也要受牵连。而且因为人家是口头招呼，所以倒霉的只有自己，那我何必冒这个风险呢", "timestamp": 1657464338}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286974, "create_time": 1657464345, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re : 我怎么记得50w以下存款本息全额赔付是法律规定的？有没有人解释下", "timestamp": 1657464345}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286989, "create_time": 1657465099, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "Re 洞主: 明天起来给你细讲 银行是地方政府的", "timestamp": 1657465099}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287137, "create_time": 1657468969, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "Re Grace: 很简单，只要咬死你这个是理财不是存款就行了，你不服又能怎样", "timestamp": 1657468969}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287145, "create_time": 1657469115, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "Re Grace: 这个要等央行定性，不知等到猴年马月去", "timestamp": 1657469115}], "create_time": 1657462392, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1657469115, "likenum": 15, "n_attentions": 15, "n_comments": 24, "pid": 81165, "poll": null, "reply": 24, "text": "#80772\n所以人们希望这件事情应该如何解决呢？应该让政府来兜底赔偿？那这笔钱应该从哪里出呢，用财政的钱去赔吗？", "timestamp": 1657462392}}